---

<div class="announcement-bar">
  <div class="announcement-inner">
    <span class="announcement-icon">🚨</span>
    <p class="announcement-text">
      El contenedor cierra en menos de una semana — aún estás a tiempo de asegurar tu espacio
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .announcement-bar {
    background-color: #000;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0 24px;
    height: 70px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }

  .announcement-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    max-width: 1152px;
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .announcement-icon {
    font-size: 22px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .announcement-text {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .announcement-bar {
      height: auto;
      padding: 12px 16px;
    }

    .announcement-text {
      font-size: 13px;
    }
  }
</style>
